The paper discusses the use of grid technologies, service-based database management, and distributed image analysis in the context of mammography data. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Databases (cs.DB), Cybersecurity (cs.CY), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), or Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) sub-categories.
